title: stay in your own lane!
itunes:title: stay in your own lane!
description:
Brooke and Danielle are opening up about some recent battles with self comparison + jealousy!  The gals needed a reminder to stay focused on themselves and their goals, and they are sharing it with you all today!  Listen in for specific tips on how to not let social media convince you everyone has it all together + so much more.  Be sure to follow and tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/stories!
